    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安裝Hexo"><a href="#安裝Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安裝Hexo"></a>安裝Hexo</h1><p><strong>1. Windows</strong>     </p>
<ol>
<li>安裝Git</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="external">Windows i386/x64 32/64bit</a></li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>安裝Node.js<br>根據你的Windos版本, 下載相對應版本  </li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v4.6.6/node-v4.6.6-x86.msi" target="_blank" rel="external">Windows i386 32bit</a>   </li>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v4.6.0/node-v4.6.0-x64.msi" target="_blank" rel="external">Windows x64 64bit</a></li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li><p>‘Win’+’R’打開執行畫面, 輸入’cmd’打開命令提示字元視窗</p>
</li>
<li><p>輸入’node -v &amp;&amp; npm -v’看版本確認安裝成功</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>2. Ubuntu</strong>  </p>
